sg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/095321_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F095321_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a06d92ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ce4a2818f41171448bd0c7f20f85a4ef7acc77d","tid":604324,"uid":98232,"like":7,"dislike":38,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:00:41.000Z","msg":"美國夠保護佢高科技產業唔開放中國啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果美國想貿易逆差減少<br />\n佢開放佢高科技產業咪得lo<br />\n中國多多錢都買<br />\n中國當年入wto係好著數<br />\n佢既規則既bug對中國好多好處<br />\n但呢條規則都係美國自己一手創立<br />\n只可以講美國佬on9 做生意唔夠中國黎<br />\n通識都有學過啦 全球化有咩好處壞處<br />\n簡單d黎講 美國企業係早幾十年全球化底下<br />\n已經搵唔少錢 賺左好多 <br />\n而家中國有錢起黎 變左全球化對佢有利<br />\n美國咪變相要貿易保護lo<br />\n唔好忘記1985年既廣場協議<br />\n當時日本同美國既貿易逆差同而家中國情況差唔多<br />\n但日本當時人均gdp仲高過美國<br />\n結果美國唔抵得日本賺左自己咁多錢<br />\n用廣場協議去課日本重稅<br />\n搞到日本經濟低迷都而家<br />\n而當年重創日本經濟既美國貿易代表羅伯特<br />\n今日又出番黎 諗住用同樣手段對付中國"},{"pid":"e06f17a687c1d1829f6de638a4f930a22e8e1b0d","tid":604324,"uid":46947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:01:30.000Z","msg":"私人企業做到有啲氣息就會被收歸國有或加插共產黨員入董事局。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0b260bcc928baef394c387c79d03a096657857","tid":604324,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:09:02.000Z","msg":"美國依家先出手已經好遲 支那已經上咗位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38558028ec3d709d01559d4adf271a256927ad41","tid":604324,"uid":30169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:09:58.000Z","msg":"五毛見字死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8120bb7294f84fb7b106b34ed798ffec6ace532","tid":604324,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b009dda808b214af196a10719521eef4af29c5","tid":604324,"uid":72963,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國夠保護佢高科技產業唔開放中國啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果美國想貿易逆差減少<br />\n佢開放佢高科技產業咪得lo<br />\n中國多多錢都買<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國當年入wto係好著數<br />\n佢既規則既bug對中國好多好處<br />\n但呢條規則都係美國自己一手創立</span><br />\n只可以講美國佬on9 做生意唔夠中國黎<br />\n通識都有學過啦 全球化有咩好處壞處<br />\n簡單d黎講 美國企業係早幾十年全球化底下<br />\n已經搵唔少錢 賺左好多 <br />\n而家中國有錢起黎 變左全球化對佢有利<br />\n美國咪變相要貿易保護lo<br />\n唔好忘記1985年既廣場協議<br />\n當時日本同美國既貿易逆差同而家中國情況差唔多<br />\n但日本當時人均gdp仲高過美國<br />\n結果美國唔抵得日本賺左自己咁多錢<br />\n用廣場協議去課日本重稅<br />\n搞到日本經濟低迷都而家<br />\n而當年重創日本經濟既美國貿易代表羅伯特<br />\n今日又出番黎 諗住用同樣手段對付中國</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國有冇遵守過人地定既規則??"},{"pid":"49dcaa52bb308821436cf82cc6b889e59de13728","tid":604324,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"a3b009dda808b214af196a10719521eef4af29c5","tid"